creator: Tiger Properties
descriptionHtml: Tiger Customer Services App helps tenants and landlords to submit suggestions, complains and requests easily and keep track of the requests, pay fees online, communicate with customer service department, and deal with other related issues better. *It's an online self-service to save customers time and effort*. Also, it manages all the digital customer care channels through a single platform which assembles all the interactions and requests in one place to be able to handle them more efficiently.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: We are constantly working on improving our app based on the valuable feedback. This version contains minor bug fixes to enhance your experience.

title: Customer Services

creator: Tiger Properties
descriptionHtml:
Tiger Customer Service app is a digital platform that assembles all our customer services in one place for our valuable customers in an easy and better way.
The App helps tenants, landlords, and brokers to :
• View contract, cheques, and payment details.
• Submit and track suggestions, complaints, and customer requests.
• Pay fees online.
• Communicate with the customer service department.
• Search in all our available properties.
• See projects updates
• View reports

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: We are constantly working on improving our app based on the valuable feedback. This version includes changes in designs, added new modules and some minor bug fixes to enhance your experience.
